      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't let you down? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and is ready to get you where you need to go! While it shows some character through normal wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid and reliable choice for anyone seeking practical transportation at a great value.",
