    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. The interior is clean and comfortable, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor scuffs on the plastic trim. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, but you will find a few small stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches near the door handles. It is a reliable, honest car that reflects careful use and regular servicing.",
      "price": 34000.0,
