      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a truly pristine specimen. Every detail reflects a legacy of meticulous care, ensuring a driving experience that remains indistinguishable from new. This is an investment-grade vehicle for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
